Encoding: UTF-8
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Regression Models using 'Stan'
Version: 2.3.0
Date: 2018-05-14
Authors@R: person("Paul-Christian", "B端rkner", email = "paul.buerkner@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0), Rcpp (>= 0.12.0), ggplot2 (>= 2.0.0), methods
